00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:30,620
Instead, friction completely reinterprets the mechanism underlying the math.

465
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:34,120
They use a branch of mathematics called sheaf theory to do this.

466
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:40,100
For the listener, we need to carefully walk through what sheaf theory is because it is the engine for the rest of the deep dive.

